<Defs>
  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
    <defName>JeubCaller</defName>
    <label>Jeubcaller</label>
    <description>The Jeubcaller is an unique caste of Jeub in a Jeub Hive. Distinguished at birth by its golden color and horn-like tongue, Jeubcallers display their unique behavior when not present at the actual base of the hive. They will periodically summon other feral Jeubs in order to assist them in foraging food to take home. It takes approximately one and one-half days for a Jeubcaller to summon more feral Jeubs. Jeubcallers are not predatory hunters and will only attack if struck first.</description>
